/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/planner.md:7:- Prior work already isolated the three load-bearing exact-NS pressures on the idea: coefficient rigidity, unavoidable spectator couplings, and exact projection/reality bookkeeping.
