/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-01.md:9:In exact Navier-Stokes, those channels arise from one helical/Fourier interaction law whose coefficients are rigid functions of triad geometry, helicity signs, and Leray projection. The route is to show that a minimal exact packet cannot realize the required hierarchy with the needed sign pattern.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-01.md:15:- a proposition-scale impossibility statement for a minimal exact helical packet that tries to implement Tao's five roles; or
