+# Exploration 001 Report
+
+## Goal
+
+Separate Tao-circuit features that are genuinely load-bearing for this mission
+branch from features that are merely convenient packaging, while keeping clear
+boundaries between Tao's internal mechanism, exact-NS mismatch claims, and
+Step-1 scope-lock commitments.
+
+## Method
+
+- Read the required source anchors first.
+- Extract direct claims about the Tao mechanism and the branch's testing frame.
+- Classify each target feature as `essential`, `dispensable`, or `open but load-bearing`.
+- Mark major conclusions as `[VERIFIED]`, `[INFERRED]`, or `[PROPOSED]`.
+- Record dead ends and ambiguities instead of forcing false certainty.
+
+## Working Notes
